we're talking about Otto may have been Otto may have been the first person to have realized that you could license the use of a photograph and you still had the photograph I mean the whole sense of oh wait a minute you mean I sold it and I still have it I think he really so in a way he is and without really owning it either well also without even owning it that's right I mean you can

